name: Fancy Bones- Porous necklace large
description:
Hand-forged whitened or oxidized sterling Silver and 18 Kt yellow Gold. The skeletal system, as scaffolding that supports and protects organs and its structural beauty are paralleled in these delicate 18 Kt gold and whitened silver pieces. The dichotomies of strength/fragility and industrial/organic, are the foundations for this hand-made collection, dedicated to my miraculously mobile mother and her new hips.
Just as each body is unique, each piece is hand-forged and one of a kind, with no two necklaces having the exact same structure.
